[node name="NoteHolder" type="Node3D" parent="."]

[node name="ReadableNote" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(-1, 0, -8.742278e-08, 0, 1, 0, 8.742278e-08, 0, -1, -9, 3.5, -36.01)
text = "Your mission is to retrieve fuel tanks and refill the generator. There are five fuel tanks in total, each is heavy and only one can be carried at a time. When the moon sets, the blizzard will roll in and snuff out your light and only hope. If you fail, it would mean the end for humanity. Should you succeed, you shall be heralded as a hero for the new age. Good luck."

[node name="ReadableNote2" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(-1, 0, 8.940697e-08, 0, 1, 0, -8.940697e-08, 0, -1, -81, 3.5, -30.01)
text = "This is our fate, this is what we deserve. I looked over the walls, into the wind and storm. There's nothing left, only the tower of cryopods, barely even half full anymore. How long has it been? How many people have been sent out here only to freeze and die, or to die at the hands of that thing in here with us? That creature, it is righteousness, is it justice, it is consequences. This is the Fimbulwinter before Ragnarok, and that thing is the great wolf Fenrir, here to bring the end."

[node name="ReadableNote3" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 20, 3.5, -79.990005)
text = "I saw some notes out in the area. They were in some odd dead end areas with not much nearby. I didn't see much point in checking them out, but I sure wish I did now. I'm not sure who or what left them, but it sure makes me wonder why. Are there still people trying to survive out here? What if I ain't the first one to be sent out here? Just in case, I'll leave some of my own."

[node name="ReadableNote4" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, -34, 3.5, -79.990005)
text = "It has been exactly ------- years since the Cold Snap began. They're predictin' that a pretty bad storm's about to come through. One that'll take us all out. So, they've been sending people out here whenever the generator's busted. If this thing's supposed to power the thing that saves us, I'd've hoped it'd be a bit more reliable than this. Well, I'm writing this note in case the generator gets busted again after I've fixed it. Hope these'll help."

[node name="ReadableNote5" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(-1, 0, -8.742278e-08, 0, 1, 0, 8.742278e-08, 0, -1, -5, 3.5, -8.01)
text = "The cryo pods. Those are our tickets to freedom from this godforsaken weather. Supposed to keep us all alive for thousands of years to weather out the storm. Wait until Earth is habitable again. That's good. We don't need to fuck it up any more than we have. I just need to get through this. I just need to fix the generator. Then everything will be okay."

[node name="ReadableNote6" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(-4.371139e-08, 0, -1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, -4.371139e-08, -30.01, 3.5, -37)
text = "That… that thing chased me, got me real bad. I don't know how long I can manage. Only one more. Only one more can of fuel to get before fixing the generator. And then I'm free. Then we'll all be free."

[node name="ReadableNote7" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(-4.371139e-08, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, -1, 0, -4.371139e-08, -15.99, 3.5, -32)
text = "I swear I saw something in the shadows. Some sort of… cloaked figure? Maybe? I think I saw… fangs. Maybe the cold's getting to me. Whatever— I've found two cans of fuel. There should be two more. I can do this. I hope the generator doesn't break after this. But it should be fine, this is a one-time freak incident Regardless, I'm gonna' move more quietly from here on, I don't want to draw attention."

[node name="ReadableNote8" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, -47, 3.5, -50.1)
text = "My name's H. Billy from Bumfunkville USA! I don't know where I am, but I thought I'd write on this note. It's awfully warm today, but I hear there's a cold whatsit approaching! Good thing I gots my windbreaker!"
metadata/_edit_group_ = true

[node name="ReadableNote9" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 59, 3.5, -20.1)
text = "They said I'd just have to go on a quick run to fix the generator, it was supposed to save everyone. I was gonna be a hero. Now they sent me out here again. It's broken again, they lied to me. There's new bodies here too. It's been years. It's worse than ever, they lied-- they lied-- they lied. It's never getting better, there's nothing, nothing but waiting for the generator to finally run out forever"

[node name="ReadableNote10" parent="NoteHolder" instance=ExtResource("13_1te7l")]
transform = Transform3D(-1, 0, 8.940697e-08, 0, 1, 0, -8.940697e-08, 0, -1, 37, 3.5, -63.99)
text = "People used to think about fixing the climate, but I don't think much ever really got done 'bout it. Now it's all cold and they're saying that's the same thing as what made all those big storms down south. Whole planet seems pissed at us now. They're saying everything south of the Great Lakes is uninhabitable, though it ain't much better up here to my eye."

